OL,6,FAt the start of the year, four
OL,7,Fcommissioners were appointed to
OL,8,Foversee changes at South Wales Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Service after a and racism
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FIn the committee, the FBU's national
OL,13,Fexecutive member was asked by Plaid
OL,14,FCymru MS, Sioned Williams, about fire
OL,15,Fstaff's confidence in the next steps
OL,16,Ffor the fire service.
OL,18,FShe asked, "How confident are you that
OL,19,Fthe views of (firefighter and control
OL,20,Froom staff) are being heard by the
OL,21,FWelsh Government?"
