OL,6,F"Staff said that nobody was listening,
OL,7,Fthat it was just a tick box exercise
OL,8,Fand they're just there to introduce
OL,9,Fthe changes that are required and they
OL,10,Fdon't want to listen to worker's
OL,11,Fvoices and that's what staff were
OL,12,Fbringing back to us."
OL,14,FITV Wales understands that Vij
OL,15,FRandeniya, who is one of the four
OL,16,FSouth Wales commissioners, visited the
OL,17,Fservices' control room on Tuesday 27
OL,18,FFebruary.
