OL,6,FMr Randeniya, who is the fire and
OL,7,Frescue services' lead commissioner,
OL,8,Fsaid his visit was "constructive and
OL,9,Fwide ranging". He added, "I am
OL,10,Fsurprised to hear that staff have
OL,11,Fgiven negative feedback to the union."
OL,13,FHowever, a control room-insider told
OL,14,Fus the commissioner's visit was
OL,15,F"disrespectful."
OL,17,FThe committee also heard how unions
OL,18,Fwere not consulted on the appointment
OL,19,Fof Interim Chief Fire Officer, Stuart
OL,20,FMillington.
