OL,6,FIn February it was revealed that Mr
OL,7,FMillington was himself at the centre
OL,8,Fof bullying allegations himself, which
OL,9,Flead to the union deciding in him as
OL,10,Finterim chief
OL,12,F"How was that decision made?", said
OL,13,FMatt Wrack, General Secretary of the
OL,14,FFBU. "We have had no involvement nor
OL,15,Fdiscussion nor consultation about the
OL,16,Fappointment of Mr Millington."
OL,18,FITV Wales has approached the
OL,19,Fcommissioners and South Wales Fire and
OL,20,FRescue for a statement.
